00134 Object *rna_Main_objects_new(Main *UNUSED(bmain), ReportList *reports, const char *name, ID *data)
00135 {
00136     Object *ob;
00137     int type = OB_EMPTY;
00138     if (data) {
00139         switch (GS(data->name)) {
00140             case ID_ME:
00141                 type = OB_MESH;
00142                 break;
00143             case ID_CU:
00144                 type = curve_type((struct Curve *)data);
00145                 break;
00146             case ID_MB:
00147                 type = OB_MBALL;
00148                 break;
00149             case ID_LA:
00150                 type = OB_LAMP;
00151                 break;
00152             case ID_SPK:
00153                 type = OB_SPEAKER;
00154                 break;
00155             case ID_CA:
00156                 type = OB_CAMERA;
00157                 break;
00158             case ID_LT:
00159                 type = OB_LATTICE;
00160                 break;
00161             case ID_AR:
00162                 type = OB_ARMATURE;
00163                 break;
00164             default:
00165             {
00166                 const char *idname;
00167                 if (RNA_enum_id_from_value(id_type_items, GS(data->name), &idname) == 0)
00168                     idname = "UNKNOWN";
00169 
00170                 BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "ID type '%s' is not valid for a object", idname);
00171                 return NULL;
00172             }
00173         }
00174 
00175         id_us_plus(data);
00176     }
00177 
00178     ob = add_only_object(type, name);
00179     id_us_min(&ob->id);
00180 
00181     ob->data = data;
00182     test_object_materials(ob->data);
00183     
00184     return ob;
00185 }
